snippet.title: My Demonic Romance Trailer - Now on Kickstarter!
snippet.description:
Here is the trailer for our supernatural visual novel My Demonic Romance!
We are currently funding it on Kickstarter, come help us make it a reality and have fun with Lily and her friends!
https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/andrealphus/my-demonic-romance-lose-your-soul-or-find-your-soulmate
